{
  "stem": "3040.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And sometimes we used to get visitors come over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The distances are very short.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "People lived either next door or next street, and used to come over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At other times, we would go to visit the others and spent a few hours Friday night like an oneg Shabbat that you know here.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, Shabbat morning, like every good Jew, goes to shul.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We went to the rebbe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we spent between three and four hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My father was also musically inclined.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he was-- he had a good voice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So sometimes he performed the services of the shaliach tzibbur, like the hazzan here, the cantor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this was not a profession for him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It just was an amateurish thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In fact, I do this too today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, Pesach didn't start Erev Pesach.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pesach started two weeks before Pesach.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is when you took apart the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not only-- you were actually looking to clean every, every corner, every little-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how to express this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, it was something that it took, really, weeks to prepare for because we were very strict with regard to chametz, not to have chametz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not only the house, but all of the books that we had in our closets and on the shelves were taken out to the yard, And shaken in case that somebody would use it during a meal during the year.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And maybe some crumbs would get into it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we used to shake out these books so that they would be free of chametz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then of course a whole week, eight days of Pesach followed with all the traditions, with the-- with the seder, where we used to have all these people to come to our seder.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
